Project 1-1

Email Application

Scenario:
An IT Support Administration Specialist and are charged with the task of creating email accounts
for accounts for new hires.

Your Application should do the following:

* Generate an email with the following syntax: firstname.lastname@department.company.com
* Determine the department (sales, development, and accounting), if none leave blank
* Generate a random String for a password
* Have a set method to change a password, set the mailbox capacity and define an alternative
  email address.
* Have a get method to display the name, email, and mailbox capacity
